  <string name="policy_adpartners_title">Ad Partners Privacy</string>
  <string name="policy_privacy_content">Your privacy is important to us. Aboneliklerim does not collect, sell, or share your personal subscription details. All subscription data, costs, and contact lists are stored locally on your device or optionally backed up securely in your private Google Firebase account under your authenticated session. We do not track your payment methods or credentials.</string>
  <string name="policy_deletion_content">Under GDPR and Google Play policies, you have complete control over your data. To permanently delete your locally stored subscription data, go to app settings and clear the application cache. If you have synced your data to the cloud, you can permanently delete all your subscription plans from the cloud by clicking \'Delete Cloud Data\'. Please note that we do not collect or store personal profiles; your login is only used for authentication, so there is no account to delete, only your subscription data can be deleted.</string>
  <string name="policy_copyright_content">© 2026 FALCON ANDROİD STUDİO. All rights reserved. Aboneliklerim is provided as a subscription tracking service. All graphics, branding, assets, source code, and design components are the intellectual property of FALCON ANDROİD STUDİO. Any unauthorized reproduction, reverse engineering, or redistribution of this software without prior consent is strictly prohibited.</string>
  <string name="policy_adpartners_content">We utilize Google AdMob to display personalized or non-personalized advertisements to support application development. Google AdMob may collect device advertising identifiers (GAID), network details, and cookies to deliver relevant ads. For more information or to manage your ad personalization, please visit Google Ad Personalization Settings inside your Android system settings.</string>

